# Replit Deployment Configuration

# RECOMMENDED: Use Reserved VM instead of Autoscale
# Reason: Your app has background processes and real-time features

# Deploy Configuration:
# 1. Change deployment type to "Reserved VM" 
# 2. Use these settings:

# Build Command: 
pip install -r requirements-prod.txt

# Run Command:
gunicorn --bind 0.0.0.0:$PORT wsgi_production:application --workers 2 --worker-class gevent

# Environment Variables needed:
# - OKX_API_KEY
# - OKX_SECRET_KEY  
# - OKX_PASSPHRASE
# - OPENAI_API_KEY
# - DATABASE_URL (auto-provided by Replit)

# Port: 
# Use $PORT (auto-provided by Replit)

# Domain:
# Will be provided automatically